Blackheart opened his stomach. His hand held the case with energon surronding 
half of Magnus' spark. "I did better then that hes under my control. Our link 
was severed for a brief time while in warp and he was able to tell Rodimus of 
the happenings...but now i once again have control over him. Ill wait till 
the time is right." He though back to the battle of Gigaton. It was his 
mightest victory, and it was were he captured the great maximal leader 
Magnus, and made him his slave.

--part1_142.2d9e7a0.2b086f04_boundary
